com.github.ltennstedt.finnmath.core.number

Class Fraction

  • Object
    • Fraction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MathNumber<Fraction,Fraction,Fraction>, Comparable<Fraction>

    @Beta
public final class Fraction
extends Object
implements MathNumber<Fraction,Fraction,Fraction>, Comparable<Fraction>
    An immutable implementation of a fraction which uses BigInteger as type for its numerator and denominator

    The returned Fractions of most methods are neither normalized nor reduced

    Since:
    1
    Author:
    Lars Tennstedt
    See Also:
    normalize(), reduce()
